twitch_info.title: Stream vom 25.01.23 - Old Glitch-Puzzle by TheBiob

message.body: yesterday i had a bug i was trying to fix, and randomly it just stopped working even more guess what happened
turns out what happened was that the IDE decided to duplicate the code i was working on and overwrote other events with it because that makes sense :) :)

and like, not even really duplicate, it just decided to overwrite the other events with a reference to the code i was working on, so whenever i was changing something in that other event, it'd also change in the other ones
which makes no sense considering the codes are stored in an xml format so ???
last time that happened i at least messed with files while the ide was running, this time i wasn't
also, said bug i was trying to fix is still not fixed
